PagineGialle,Officine/Artigiani,Varese,Binacchi e Co.,"Via Gramsci, 84 - 21045 Gazzada Schianno (VA)","0332 461354, 0332 464218",http://www.binacchi.com/,"[Home - Binacchi - Soap Line] | Home - Binacchi - Soap Line Over fifty years of excellence in soap, DETERGENT and glycerine plants We sell solutions and not simply PLANTS What we SUPPLY Saponification Plants Binacchi has a fourty-year-long experience in manufacturing continuous saponification plants and more than 100 plants are in operation around the world. The patented MPSD is world reference for Swing saponifications and more than 50 plants have been delivered in 10 years. Soap Finishing Lines The most important innovations in the matter of production of toilet soap belong to Binacchi. We are the designers of the highest speed lines, which are operating from big multinational companies to small specialty producers nearly in every country of the world. Detergent Plants In 1993 Binacchi introduced the technology for Synthetic Detergent Plants. Now we are one the world's most expert suppliers for this technology with many plants in operation. In addition, Binacchi is manufacturing components and plants for sulphonation technology as well. Packaging Machines Binacchi is the only soap machines constructor in the world manufacturing also paper wrapping machines as well as supply flowpack and cartoners and integrate secondary packaging machines. Liquid Detergents and Filling Binacchi manufactures plants for the production of liquid detergents. Since 2021, Binacchi expanded in the manufacture of filling, capping and labelling of bottles with the acquisition of Zeta S.r.l. , a company with particular experience in liquid detergents, chemical products and refined oils. Glycerine Plants Recovery plants either for concentrated glycerine 80-88% or distilled pharma grade 99.9%. Our equipment can process any feedstocks from soap spent lyes,fatty acids sweet waters or biodiesel crude glycerine. Exhibitions The acquisition of ZETA January 2022 Binacchi & Co. announces the acquisition of Zeta S.r.l , welcoming the company in Binacchi Group. Zeta is an Italian leader in manufacturing filling, capping, labelling l",
