PagineGialle,Officine/Artigiani,Arona,Societa' Industria Meccanica S.I.Me. a Responsabilita' Limitata,"Via Arona, 82 - 28021 Borgomanero (NO)","0322 81625, 0322 282741, 0322 072016",http://www.simeccanica.it/,"[Società Industria Meccanica SIME srl – We manufacture your Dreams] | Società Industria Meccanica SIME srl – We manufacture your Dreams We manufacture your dreams Società Industria Meccanica srl dreams into reality . We are S.I.ME. S.I.ME. is a family owned Company, manufacturing complex machined components for the Aerospace & Defence market. Our parts are assembled in Actuation Systems, Landing Gears, Hydraulic & Fuel distribution Systems, advanced Defense systems, bith for fixed and rotary wings aircrafts. S.I.ME. does not represent a simple supplier, but a partner able to guarantee customers the support they need, from the early co-design stages . Innovation, flexibility and state-of-the-art technology turn dreams into value . Meet us at: HALL 1 | 1245 Watch full length video HERE Why should I choose S.I.ME. ? Because S.I.ME. is… CUSTOMER-CENTRIC Research in innovation , people experience and know in order to increase customer satisfaction SUSTAINABLE In synergy with security , quality and environmental policies. CAPABLE « Quality Over Quantity » approach, improving the capability to offer high-quality personalized solutions COOPERATIVE A virtuous collaboration network of investments and industrial partnerships aimed to respond to complexity of technology COMPLETE & QUALIFIED Direct control on all the steps of the production cycle: from raw material procurement to delivery . Extensive supply: flexible and certified in compliance with time delivery with security, quality and environmental policies. RAW MATERIAL Your general contractor for raw materials, always ready with a buffer stock for most common aerospace materials. MECHANICAL MANUFACTURING We manufacture your drawings with care, passion , precision and attitude to problem solving . MECHANICAL MANUFACTURING MANTEINANCE Discover our MRO station skills and flexibility: get real-time feedback and interaction with our custom software . MRO STATION SPECIAL PROCESSES Are you looking for a manufacturer with in-house special processes to save time and money? You are in the right place",
