PagineGialle,Hotel/B&B,Varese,54 Cat's Guesthouse,"Via Cattaneo Carlo, 54 - 21013 Gallarate (VA)",338 4301999,http://www.54cat.it/,"[54Cat - Guest House e B&B] | Comodo punto di riferimento vicino all'aereoporto di Malpensa e Milano, a due passi dalla stazione. Bed & Breakfast e Gust House perfetta per famiglie | 54Cat - Guest House e B&B About 54 CAT is a Guesthouse 500 mt far from Gallarate train station, connected to Malpensa Airport by bus, train and with a shuttle service (payable on reservation). An ideal location to travel comfortably through Lombardy, Piedmont and Switzerland, to visit Milan and Lake Maggiore or Fiera Milano Expo. 54 CAT’s structure is located inside a typical Lombard Courtyard, offers modern apartment comforts and can guest up to 6 people in two independent but communicating spaces, with reserved entrance: 1 - CAT , apartment 4 beds, 50 sqm, living room with fully equipped kitchen and sofa bed for two, bedroom with double bed, bathroom with hydromassage cabin. 2 - Kalimera Room , double room, 25 sqm, double sofa bed, TV, coffee and hot drinks machine, microwave, minibar. Exclusive external bathroom on the internal staircase with shower and washing machine. No smoking (except on the balcony) Pets not allowed Free Wi-Fi Internet Free parking on the street in front of the house Reception via Andrea Doria 5 (playing Bardelli Bossi) Check in - Check out : arrival between 16.00 and 19.00, departure before 10.00. Different needs must be agreed Languages spoken: Italian, English, French, Spanish 54 Cat is a friend of legality , is enrolled to the association BBVarese and respects the regional and national legislation of tourism, including the communication of the lodged to the police authority www.bbvarese.it Find us 54 CAT’s Guesthouse location is strategical because it allows easy access to public transport and highways. It is 500 yards far from the Gallarate railway station where buses and trains continually depart to Malpensa Airport, , Switzerland, Varese, Milan (with halfway stop Rho Fiera Milano Expo), and to Domodossola (with halfway stops Arona on Lake Maggiore and Stresa with Borromean Islands). About half a mile away you find the A8 highway Gallarate exit. The city centre and the hospital are less than 1 km far away. To get around by public trans",
