PagineGialle,Hotel/B&B,Luino,Camping Lido Toce,Via per Feriolo 41 - 28924 Verbania (VB),0323 496220,http://www.campinglidotoce.eu/,"[Camping in Italy Lido Toce] | A campsite close to nature on Lago Maggiore where families are welcome, with its own beach directly on the lake, has large pitches. | Camping in Italy Lido Toce Lido Toce Natural camping Relaxation on Lago Maggiore FOR MORE THAN 60 YEARS our campsite offers much more than just a wonderful holiday with excellent service. Lido Toce is located in the estuary of the river Toce near the Fondotoce nature reserve, with a sandy beach directly on Lake Maggiore. Experience nature in its most beautiful facets and relax from your everyday life. CAMPING ON THE SANDY BEACH Our campsite on Lake Maggiore has a fine sandy beach that invites you to sunbathe, swim and relax. The clear water of the lake delights all guests who are looking for relaxation in a wonderful setting. FAMILIAR, SYMPATHETIC & CHILD-FRIENDLY With us, you can sit back, relax and enjoy your camping holiday. Our well-maintained campsite is child-friendly, family-oriented and very pleasant. The playground is located right next to our restaurant. Children under 6 years of age are free of charge. THE CAMPSITE The campsite offers spacious pitches with 220v/6a electricity supply. The new toilets, the handicapped-accessible wet cells and shower rooms offer free hot water supply. Furthermore, large washrooms with washing machines and a camper service are available. MORE INFORMATION GASTRONOMY The Lido Toce minimarket is located in a new building. Here, you have the possibility to help yourself. In the Amici restaurant, we offer drinks, beer and a few cocktails, as well as small snacks to take away: Pizza, Pasta and much more. MORE INFORMATION ACTIVITIES From the beach, you have a splendid view of the Borromean Islands, Pallanza, the picturesque village of Feriolo (reachable by foot and bike path) as well as Baveno and the tourist town of Stresa, 9 km away. MORE INFORMATION LIDO TOCE MOMENTS Visit our gallery and see how beautiful our campsite and surroundings are. VISIT THE GALLERY! GIVE JOY AS A GIFT Do you want to give your friends and loved ones a special gift? Give them an unforgettable experience. TO OUR NEWS HOW TO FIND US It's easy to plan your r",
