PagineGialle,Hotel/B&B,Como,Meta S.p.a.,"Viale Masia Massenzio, 34 - 22100 Como (CO)","031 571755, 031 5378511",https://www.grandhoteltremezzo.com/,"[Grand Hotel Tremezzo: luxury 5 star hotel on Lake Como, Italy] | THE OFFICIAL SITE. The Grand Hotel Tremezzo, luxury 5 star hotel has a panoramic view of Lake Como. It also offers a spa and a very fine restaurant for a pleasant stay. | Grand Hotel Tremezzo: luxury 5 star hotel on Lake Como, Italy Discover our Boutique “That sunny, happy place” Greta Garbo in the film Grand Hotel, 1932 Welcome to a place where history, tradition and glamour play with a contemporary spirit of independence; a place where the possibilities—like the views—feel endless. GRAND THINGS Heritage Two families, one vision, shared across a century—of embracing innovation, and creating modern new traditions. Italianità From the first benvenuto! to the last aperitivo, making you feel eminently at home is something we’ve elevated to a high art. Vistas Everywhere you look is an intriguing story, framed in the Belle Epoque splendour for which we’ve always been known. Nature Wide green lawns, lush botanic gardens, verdant alfresco corners: a dazzling array of flora is yours to explore. Days that deliver endless delights Benvenuti sul Lago di Como, where unique moments of joy are yours for the having, exactly the way you want to have them The tiny village with the hidden waterfall. The path meandering through wildflower meadows and cool forests to a medieval church. The little water-side trattoria that’s the insiders’ secret. Lake Como is a kaleidoscope of only-here experiences; there never seems to be time to delight in them all. But oh, it’s fun trying. (And even better done from one of our beautiful boats.) Come and explore... Our Rooms & Suites Havens of Indulgence Fine prints and gleaming antiques. Soft comforts, painted in rich, enchanting colors. And from every window, a sigh-provoking view out over the gleaming lake or our lush park. Our rooms and suites evince the soul of our welcome, in their every detail. Go inside... Our Private Villa With its arabesque gardens, six beautiful suites, and an aristocratic history dating back to the 16th century, Villa Sola Cabiati—reached in minutes from the hotel by car or boat—is our exclusive-booking escape, complete with a private staff to help you live out your Lake Como dream. Come be",
