nment. Private bathrooms with shower/tub combinations feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Book a room About Albergo Residence Isotta Location Via Pozzarino 1, Veruno, Piedmont, 28010, Italy See on map Sports (1) Culturals (1) Historic (1) Naturals (1) Stadio Alfredo d'Albertas Stadium 11.77 km Museo Storico Etnografico Museum 13.32 km Buccione Castle Castle 12.08 km Riserva naturale del Colle di Buccione Nature Conservation Area 12.",
