GoogleMaps,Ristoranti/Pizzerie,Luino,Agriturismo ristorante Voeuja,"Via Longhirolo, 9, 21016 Luino VA, Italia",344 267 5464,http://www.voeuja.it/,"[Agriturismo Voeuja Lago Maggiore] | Agriturismo Voeuja Lago Maggiore Welcome to Agriturismo Voeuja Restaurant with a view! Agriturismo Voeuja Local, sustainable and natural Agriturismo Voeuja Voeuja apartments we are closed during wintertime from 15 October until 1st of May From €150 / Night Apartment Lago 5 sleeps + baby bed From €135 / Night Studio - Apartment Monte Rosa 2 sleeps + baby bed From €160 / Night Apartment Orto 5 sleeps + baby bed Relax, take it easy, you're in Italy! Voeuja restaurant In 2013 we sold our restaurant 'In de keuken' in the center of Amsterdam and moved to the beautiful Ticino in the Italian part of Switzerland, and just some time later we found this beautiful place on the other side of the border and we just fell in love. It took us 5 years to buy and renovate the farm. On July 2019 we started renting out the apartments of Agriturismo Voeuja and occasionally we cooked for our guests. We hope we can make a good contribute to eating out in the area for locals and visitors from around the world. RESTAURANT Our kitchen is by far not the ordinary, as a self-taught Dutch / Flamish Chef, Jelle cooks without restrictions. His cuisine doesn't have boundaries it's open minded, sometimes traditional and sometimes unorthodox. There is only one important rule it has to be delicious! The Voeuja kitchen team makes almost everything themselves from fresh top ingredients. From our own bread, of which we grow the sourdough ourselves, to the bonbons and nougat and more. In the restaurant you can choose between 4 or 5 courses from our day menu, there is no à la carte choice. For children we offer the dishes from the current menus or we can prepare them a pasta with ingredients from our garden. LOCATION Agriturismo Voeuja is at a 5-minute drive from the center of Luino and Lake Maggiore with great views over the lake and mountains. We are open from April until November. We are located at one hour drive from Malpensa airport. Coming from direction Switzerland we can easily be reached from Exit ",Rating: 4.7/39
