e. Enjoy your stay, dear ""All"" members! Pietro Mancino, Hotel Management See more ibis Como Hotel information From May to September 2026, dinner service will be replaced by our exclusive bar menu, offering a selection of hot and cold dishes in a relaxed and informal setting. Service is available Monday through Friday, from 7 PM to 10 PM. Staff will be happy to assist you during your stay. *Please note that the dinner restaurant will be closed in August from August 1, 2026, to August ",Rating: 4.2/2268
