GoogleMaps,Hotel/B&B,Fino Mornasco,Avenue Boutique Hotel,"Piazzolo Giuseppe Terragni, 6, 22100 Como CO, Italia",031 272186,http://www.avenuehotel.it/,"[Home | Avenue Hotel] | Home | Avenue Hotel 01 Home avenuehotel 02 Hotel hospitality&services 03 Rooms comfort&design 04 Location in the heart of Como 05 Restaurants our restaurants 06 Contacts information request 07 Work with us information request Avenue hotel Piazzola Terragni, 6 22100 Como Italy T. +39 031 272186 info@avenuehotel.it it en es fr ru 中国 ELEGANCE & DESIGN IN THE HEART OF COMO Avenue Boutique Hotel is a modern 4 stars hotel located in Como, just steps from the charming lake and the main streets of the historic city center. Completely renovated in 2023 in style and decor. A Boutique Hotel entirely surrounded by the charm of the main places of our lake recalled in the 13 rooms and 4 suites. ROOMS 17 moderne camere che uniscono eleganza e funzionalità HOTEL Scopri tutti i servizi disponibili presso l'hotel RESTAURANTS Avenue Bistrot un menù contemporaneo, ricco di prodotti locali Pinzimonio di fronte all'hotel, nel cuore del Centro storico IN THE HEART OF COMO, JUST STEPS FROM ALL ITS BEAUTIES Como Cathedral Como Cathedral Only 250 meters on foot from the hotel you can visit the famous Duomo of Como with its cathedral. The Cathedral, begun in 1396, was completed in 1744. It is an articulated and complex architecture, which blends different interpretations of space and different stylistic expressions in a single building. main distances San Fedele Square San Fedele Square 100 meters from the hotel the wonderful Piazza S. Fedele, with its Romanesque-Baroque style Basilica. Ancient market square until the 1800s, today a lively pedestrian area frequented for shopping and tourism, also thanks to the characteristic antiques and handicraft market that populates it every Saturday. main distances Porta torre Porta torre 350 meters from the hotel there is Porta Torre. An imposing medieval fortress whose walls surround the entire historic center of Como, Porta Torre, with its 40 meters of height, is an extraordinary example of military architecture of the Romanesque tradition. main dista",Rating: 4.6/494
